## DISCLAIMER

This software is provided "AS IS" without any warranty of any kind, either
expressed or implied, including but not limited to the implied warranties of
merchantability and fitness for a particular purpose.

### Safety Warning

⚠️ **IMPORTANT:**

Quadcopter motors and propellers can cause serious injury. This project should
only be used by individuals with proper knowledge and experience in robotics
and aerospace engineering.

Users of this software:
- Assume all risks associated with its use
- Must conduct thorough safety testing before any flight operations
- Must follow all local regulations and laws regarding UAV operation
- Must ensure adequate insurance coverage
- Agree that the authors and contributors are not liable for any injury or damage

### Before Every Flight:
✅ Check all mechanical connections
✅ Verify motor rotation directions
✅ Ensure propellers are correctly installed
✅ Test RC control channels
✅ Verify battery voltage
✅ Calibrate sensors
✅ Conduct ground tests

